OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with the chance of an
OL,6,Fodd shower in the south at first
OL,7,Fotherwise a mostly dry day with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells. Cloud will increase
OL,9,Fas rain spreads into the west in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly dry with bright or
OL,13,Fclear spells in the north and the
OL,14,Feast. Cloudy with rain at times in the
OL,15,Fwest and the south.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with patchy rain in the
OL,18,Fsouth and west at first otherwise
OL,19,Fmostly dry with bright spells and the
OL,20,Fodd inland afternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
